### ============================================================
### BFF: Events — public read API
###
### Read-only, no auth. The list defaults to upcoming events
### (event_date >= today) ordered by date, then start time.
### Slug format: {date}-{venue}-{title}
### ============================================================

### List upcoming events (default page 0, size 20, sort eventDate)
GET {{bff-host}}/events
Accept: application/json

> {%
    client.test("status is 200", function () {
        client.assert(response.status === 200, "Expected 200 OK");
    });
    // Capture the first slug so the detail request below resolves to a real event.
    if (response.body.content.length > 0) {
        client.global.set("event_slug", response.body.content[0].slug);
    }
%}

### List events — pagination + sort (eventDate desc)
GET {{bff-host}}/events?page=0&size=5&sort=eventDate,desc
Accept: application/json

### List events — sort by presale price ascending
GET {{bff-host}}/events?sort=pricePresale,asc
Accept: application/json

### Filter by date range
GET {{bff-host}}/events?from=2026-06-19&to=2026-07-15
Accept: application/json

### Filter by venue slug
GET {{bff-host}}/events?venue=lido
Accept: application/json

### Filter by artist slug
GET {{bff-host}}/events?artist=actors
Accept: application/json

### Filter by genre slug
GET {{bff-host}}/events?genre=punk
Accept: application/json

### Filter by price range
GET {{bff-host}}/events?minPrice=10&maxPrice=40
Accept: application/json

### Free-text search over title + subtitle
GET {{bff-host}}/events?q=punk
Accept: application/json

### Exclude sold-out events
GET {{bff-host}}/events?excludeSoldOut=true
Accept: application/json

### Combined filters + pagination
GET {{bff-host}}/events?venue=lido&from=2026-06-19&page=0&size=10&sort=eventDate,asc
Accept: application/json

### Today's events
GET {{bff-host}}/events/today
Accept: application/json

### Calendar — events within an inclusive date range (max 92 days)
GET {{bff-host}}/events/calendar?from=2026-06-19&to=2026-07-15
Accept: application/json

### Calendar — inverted range (expect 400)
GET {{bff-host}}/events/calendar?from=2026-07-15&to=2026-06-19
Accept: application/json

### Get event by slug (uses the slug captured from the list request above)
GET {{bff-host}}/events/{{event_slug}}
Accept: application/json

### Get event by unknown slug (expect 404)
GET {{bff-host}}/events/does-not-exist
Accept: application/json
